[I] The blessed package to manage your versions by scm tags

[T] Setuptools-scm extracts Python package versions from git or
[T] hg metadata instead of declaring them as the version argument
[T] or in a Source Code Managed (SCM) managed file.

[U] https://github.com/pypa/setuptools_scm

